tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE quantum_usage (
    user_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    quantum_resource_id INT,
    usage_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    usage_data JSONB
)

CREATE TABLE QuantumTasks (
    task_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    task_name VARCHAR(255),
    task_description TEXT,
    node_id INT,
    start_time TIMESTAMP,
    end_time TIMESTAMP,
    FOREIGN KEY (node_id) REFERENCES QuantumNodes(node_id)
);

CREATE TABLE Quantum_Usage_Logs (
    log_id INT,
    resource_id INT,
    user_id INT,
    usage_type VARCHAR(50),
    usage_timestamp TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE Quantum_Usage_Log (
    log_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    resource_id INT NOT NULL,
    user_id INT NOT NULL,
    start_time DATETIME NOT NULL,
    end_time DATETIME NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE quantum_usage (
    usage_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    resource_id UUID REFERENCES quantum_resources(resource_id),
    user_id UUID REFERENCES quantum_users(user_id),
    start_time TIMESTAMP,
    end_time TIMESTAMP
);
